data.description: Single Family Home for sale by owner in Bossier City, LA 71112. This is a 3 bedroom, 2 bath, 1999 site built home that was totally gutted and remodeled in 2008. It has a spacious 500 square foot living room with cathedral ceilings and a stone, gas-burning fireplace; a 500 square foot game room perfect for a pool table. It has a 2 car garage, dual climate heat/air system, large attic, 470 square foot wooden deck in back yard, sprinkler system, 1000 square foot shop/pavilion, a large back yard with 2-year-old peach trees/nectarine trees/blueberry bushes, and 250 feet of bayou frontage (Red Chute) that is capable of launching any size boat--great fishing! It is conveniently located to Barksdale Air Force Base (approx. 7 min). NEGOTIABLES: Mineral rights B7100 Kubota tractor with bush hog/box blade/carry rack 12 foot pool table Washer/Dryer Gas Grill Stand-up Freezer 6 Armoire Open House: 6/19/2011 2pm - 4pm Virtual Tour: http://youtu.be/sXovNldzbuc
